law.history: Repealed 2006 Ky. Acts ch. 242, sec. 64, effective July 12, 2006. -- Amended 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 77, sec. 10-106. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1908.
